{"about_the_game":"<br><br>A fast-paced competitive farming game for up to 8 players online! Sabotage and steal while defending your crops and animals to become the best farmer! Team up with others or play on your own!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Plant or steal, your choice!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/FastPaced600_3.gif?t=1728014111\" /><br>Plant on your farm or steal from your friend, the important thing is to sell as much as possible.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defend your farm at all costs!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/Gif600.gif?t=1728014111\" /><br>Rely on a variety of defensive items to keep invaders away! From scarecrows to electric fences, defensive items can save your crops and animals from a thieving player. Sometimes, the best offense is defense!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Beware of random events!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/RandomEvents_Steam.gif?t=1728014111\" /><br>At every farm, you'll encounter different events that change the game's dynamics \u2013 from a shark attack to a treasure hunt, or even a zombie invasion! Just watch out for lightning strikes while you're busy selling your friend's crops!<br><br>The team that accumulates the most coins at the end of the game wins, whether by sabotage or not!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose your character!</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/extras/ChangingCharacters600_2.gif?t=1728014111\" /><br>Choose the character that best suits you!","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1285270?t=1728014111","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285270/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1728014111","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c